# SHIPKIT FRAMEWORK FILES
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# This .gitignore works for BOTH Shipkit and Shipkit Lite editions

# Framework Infrastructure (ignore - these are installed, not created by you)
.claude/
CLAUDE.md

# Full Shipkit - Scripts/Templates/References (ignore - framework infrastructure)
.shipkit/scripts/
.shipkit/skills/*/scripts/
.shipkit/skills/*/templates/
.shipkit/skills/*/references/

# IMPORTANT: DO NOT IGNORE YOUR WORK PRODUCTS!
# ✅ Shipkit Lite: .shipkit-lite/ contains YOUR context files (commit these!)
# ✅ Full Shipkit: .shipkit/skills/*/outputs/ contains YOUR work product (commit these!)
#
# These files represent your product discovery, specs, plans, and decisions.
# They should be committed to git so your team has shared context.

